data.description: Charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home on spacious corner lot. Enjoy fully fenced yard with gated RV parking! Across the street from new state of the art Lexington elementary school! Interior paint recently refreshed. Exterior recently painted! This delightful home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and space for all. With laminate floors through out the main floor & hardwood floors on the 2nd floor, open kitchen concept, upstairs laundry room, built in vacuum and lots of room to entertain. Pride in ownership shown! All kitchen appliances staying!This home is a rare find, combining functionality and comfort with a generous outdoor space.
